    {
        "source_sentence": "行復本遍住時，第三重犯是前罪類，亦復覆藏，已從僧伽乞行隨覆藏日重收根本遍住，僧伽已與鄔陀夷苾芻於前罪類隨覆藏日，重收根本遍住。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481b27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此鄔陀夷苾芻故泄精犯僧伽伐尸沙罪，隨覆藏日善行遍住。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481b28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二重犯是前罪類，復本遍住，亦復善行。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481b29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三重犯是前罪類，重收根本遍住，亦復善行。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已從僧伽乞行六夜摩那𭅤，僧伽已與鄔陀夷苾芻六夜行竟，今從僧伽乞出罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若僧伽時至聽者，僧伽應許僧伽今與鄔陀夷苾芻出罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "白如是。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「次後應作如是訶責：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝鄔陀夷苾芻應知有二種人，能滅法炬、掩法光明、壞法燈焰。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為二？",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂犯罪已不如法悔除，此即名為二小、二癡，二不明、二不善。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c09_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有二種重罪根本不肯穿掘，於逆流事不勤用功，於諸瀑流不欲乾竭，不共魔戰、不折魔旗，勝妙法幢無心建立，罪惡之見不為斷除，不於大師無上正教隨轉法輪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有二種苦毒所惱、復有二種增長有流，謂犯罪已不如法悔。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝鄔陀夷！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如世尊說：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於欲瞋癡常思遠離。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」汝今何故作斯醜事？",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝愚癡人！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何將此兩手，受他淨心所有惠施，如何還將兩手作醜惡事？",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又汝癡人！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寧將兩手捉囓毒等可畏毒蛇，不故捉生支梵云鴦伽社哆，譯作生支，即是根也為醜惡事。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c19_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝鄔陀夷！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c19_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由於犯罪不說除故，退失無常想、無常苦想、苦無我想、厭離食想、於諸世間作不樂想、過患想、是可斷想、不可愛想、滅死想、不淨想、青瘀想、膿流想、破爛想、膖脹想、血流想、狼藉想、白骨想、空觀想，如是事想皆不現前，亦不得初靜慮、二、三、四靜慮、慈悲喜捨、空處、識處、無所有處、非想非非想處、預流果、一來果、不還果阿羅漢果，悉皆不得神境通，天眼、天耳通、他心差別，宿住死生盡諸有流，皆不證會。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c28_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝鄔陀夷！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0481c29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由不說罪，命終之後，當於二道隨一受生，是怖畏處，謂捺洛迦、傍生。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如世尊說：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「二障覆業能向捺洛迦、傍生趣，由不信我言覆藏其罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」』如是慇懃作訶責已，冀令改悔。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次作羯磨：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『大德僧伽聽！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此鄔陀夷苾芻故泄精犯僧伽伐尸沙罪，半月覆藏。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此鄔陀夷苾芻已從僧伽乞隨覆藏日行遍住法，僧伽已與鄔陀夷苾芻故泄精犯僧伽伐尸沙罪隨覆藏日遍住。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行遍住時，第二重犯是前罪類，亦復覆藏。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已從僧伽乞行隨覆藏日復本遍住，僧伽已與鄔陀夷苾芻於前罪類隨覆藏日復本遍住。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行復本遍住時，第三重犯是前罪類亦復覆藏，已從僧伽乞行隨覆藏日重收根本遍住，僧伽已與鄔陀夷苾芻於前罪類隨覆藏日重收根本遍住。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此鄔陀夷於故泄精犯僧伽伐尸沙罪，隨覆藏日善行遍住。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二重犯是前罪類，復本遍住，亦復善行。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三重犯是前罪類，重收根本遍住亦復善行。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已從僧伽乞行六夜摩那𭅤，僧伽已與鄔陀夷苾芻六夜摩那𭅤，亦善行竟。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今從僧伽乞出罪，僧伽今與鄔陀夷苾芻故泄精犯僧伽伐尸沙罪隨覆藏日善行遍住。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第二重犯是前罪類，復本遍住，亦復善行。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第三重犯是前罪類，重收根本遍住，亦復善行。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六夜摩那𭅤，亦善行竟，今從僧伽乞出罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸具壽聽與鄔陀夷苾芻出罪者默然，若不許者說。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是初羯磨。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』第二、第三亦如是說。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『僧伽已與鄔陀夷苾芻出罪竟。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧伽已聽許，由其默然故，我今如是持。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a28_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「次當如是讚喻：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善哉鄔陀夷！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "極善鄔陀夷！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482a29_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有二種聰慧人、有二分明人、有二種善人。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何謂為二？",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、不犯罪；",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二、犯已能如法悔除。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有二種人能然法炬、建立法幢。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何謂為二？",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一謂不犯罪，二犯已能如法悔除。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有二種重罪根本能為穿掘，於逆流事而勤用功，於諸瀑流能使乾竭，能與魔戰，能折魔旗，勝妙法幢能善建立，罪惡之見能為斷除，能於大師無上正教隨轉法輪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為二？",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一謂不犯罪，二設犯罪已如法悔除。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有二種非苦所惱，復有二種不增有流。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為二？",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、不犯罪；",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二、犯已能悔。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝鄔陀夷！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝已說悔眾罪，是應合得無常想、無常苦想，廣說乃至能盡有流。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝於人天二道定得無疑。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如世尊說：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「有二種不覆障業，便能趣向人天二道，能信我言不覆其罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是應知，汝鄔陀夷已出罪竟，勿為放逸，於諸善品常為修習。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』若更有犯者，應如鄔陀夷苾芻次第作法。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次於出罪之後，應從僧伽乞悔窣吐羅底野罪，如是應乞。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『大德僧伽聽！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我某甲苾芻，於故泄精有前方便窣吐羅底野罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我某甲今從僧伽乞說悔法，願大德僧伽聽我某甲說悔窣吐羅底野罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是能愍者，願哀愍故。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』第二、第三亦如是說。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次一苾芻先作白，方為羯磨：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『大德僧伽聽！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此苾芻某甲，於故泄精有前方便窣吐羅底野罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此某甲今從僧伽乞說悔窣吐羅底野罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b26_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若僧伽時至聽者，僧伽應許僧伽今與某甲於故泄精有前方便窣吐羅底野罪說悔。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "白如是。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』次作羯磨：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『大德僧伽聽！",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482b29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此苾芻某甲於故泄精，有前方便窣吐羅底野罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此某甲今從僧伽乞說悔窣吐羅底野罪，僧伽今與某甲於故泄精有前方便窣吐羅底野罪說悔。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c03_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸具壽聽與某甲於故泄精有前方便窣吐羅底野罪說悔者默然，若不許者說。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是初羯磨。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』第二、第三亦如是說。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『僧伽已與某甲於故泄精，有前方便窣吐羅底野罪，聽說悔竟。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧伽已聽許，由其默然故，我今如是持。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「次後還同如是次第，所有先因眾多突色訖里多罪，及以眾多不敬教波逸底迦罪，對一苾芻如法除悔。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "窣吐羅底野罪有二種：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一謂波羅市迦因罪，二謂僧伽伐尸沙因罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於波羅市迦因復有二種：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、重，二、輕。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中重者應從大眾說悔其罪大眾者，謂界內盡集。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "言輕者下至四人，壇場中當說其罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧伽伐尸沙因罪亦有二種：",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一、重，一、輕。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此中重者上至四人壇場應說其罪，輕者應對一人如法除罪。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "波逸底迦、突色訖里多前因之罪，准前應作，眾多大小覆藏之罪，咸應說悔。",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」根本說一切有部百一羯磨卷第六",
        "from": "T24n1453_006:0482c20_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]